## Eskimo Zeppelin ElasticSearch Demo
In order to run the queries from this demo, you need to have the "Sample flight data" from Kibana addedd to elasticsearch.

(For this, just go to Kibana and follow : Add Data to Kibana / Add sample data / Load a data set and a Kibana dashboard / Install "Sample flight data")

With this data properly loaded, you can execute the paragraphs below
